some do not recognize

684
01:00:49,779 --> 01:00:51,804
the impossibility of it.

685
01:00:53,216 --> 01:00:55,241
You're wrong.

686
01:00:55,284 --> 01:00:57,411
Every man
has God within him.

687
01:00:57,487 --> 01:01:00,149
Fortunately,

688
01:01:00,223 --> 01:01:02,885
most people
don't recognize this.

689
01:01:05,361 --> 01:01:08,330
There is no essence
beneath appearance,

690
01:01:08,398 --> 01:01:10,730
only a series
of appearances,

691
01:01:10,800 --> 01:01:12,734
each rising
out of the one before

692
01:01:12,802 --> 01:01:14,736
